Package it.polimi.ingsw.view.GUI

Class ClientGui

java.lang.Object
javafx.application.Application
it.polimi.ingsw.view.GUI.ClientGui
public class ClientGui extends javafx.application.Application
This class implements GUI graphics and create the command to insert into the queue guiEvents. Createdcommand is the command created by client's actions.
